Bank / Portugal sets new variable rate repo . The Bank of Portugal offered to inject a further 30 billion escudos of seven - day funds into the money market in a variable rate securities repurchase tender . The offer was in addition to the 280 billion escudos already offered when the Bank set conditions on Thursday for Monday ' s start of a new commercial bank reserve period . The rate on the 280 billion escudo repo was 6 . 0019 percent . Bids for the additional repo funds must be submitted by 0900 GMT . - - Lisbon bureau 3511 - 3150035 
